profile:
We started The Drafting Table with one goal in mind: Creating beautiful, practical designs. From meeting with clients, to creating the design, and finally to getting the necessary permits, we will ensure you have the design, zoning approvals and municipal permits you need for your project.
We feel it is vital to deliver a product that meets your expectations and emphasizes on the details and features that are important to you.
